definitions.definition: A person or institution who processes things (foods, photos, applications, etc.).
examples: He is a loan processor with a bank.

definitions.definition: A device which processes , which changes something (a computer processor , food processor , etc.).
examples: The food processor shredded the vegetables.
This computer has two processors , but only one keyboard.
